Results.ReviewText: Although I also enjoy Tea, Coffee has always been my favorite drink. I have drank coffee from all over the world, and never go for cheaper options. I have always gone for quality, and nothing beats the taste of Nescafe Original
Results.Title: My Favorite Cuppa

Results.ReviewText: I don't think Nescafé Original can be beaten. Add boiling water, a little milk and drink before it cools to much and you have the perfect instant. I have tried other coffees but always revert back to original Nescafé perfection
Results.Title: Nescafe at its best

Results.ReviewText: I like to make coffee with milk and when added to hot milk this dissolves into the drink so much better than many other coffees. I also find that I use less because it is a little stronger making the jar last longer. Excellent
Results.Title: Excellent

Results.ReviewText: Nescafe Original, you get what you pay for. Not the cheapest, not the most expensive. Just the very best for consistent excellent taste and quality. I do of course drink mine black, no sugar, Au Naturel. What more can I say!!
Results.Title: ONLY THE BEST

Results.ReviewText: It's my first drink of the day and it's what keeps me going thru the day good cup of coffee and I can rely on nescafe for that tried others but always comes back to this one taste quality and value is always there when needed
Results.Title: Taste

Results.ReviewText: I have always been making ice cold coffee during summer and Nescafe Red is just the absolute winner. Cold water, Nescafe and sugar in the shaker and ice to top the glass up. The only way to beat the hot summer days in UK :)
Results.Title: Great instant coffee on ice!

Results.ReviewText:
I have a coffee machine and fresh coffee normally, so I know not to judge it against a fresh brew!
But as a instant, it is one of the nicest cuppa's out there. Sometimes I double up on the spoonfuls to get a bigger hit!...
Results.Title: No Fresh Brew! but my first choice for Instant Cup

Results.ReviewText: I love Nescafe Original as I know I am guaranteed the same rich roast coffee time and time again. No matter where or when, I can rely on Nescafe Original to satisfy my thirst and lift my spirits with its rich rounded taste.
Results.Title: Consistant taste time and time again.

Results.ReviewText: Have been drinking Nescafe for over 50 years, must admit I have tried others, but nothing compares to the quality and taste of Nescafe, Love the aroma of it , especially first thing in the morning, Lovely start to the day.
Results.Title: Fantastic tasting coffee.

Results.ReviewText: Been buying Original for many years, and it never fails to give me the good taste I expect.  So easy to make and as I drink it black, very quick.  Have tried others but always gone back to Nescafé. It gives me what I want.
Results.Title: Consistently reliable

Results.ReviewText: I buy refills as packaging is easily recyclable and it works out better value.  Consistent smooth Nescafe taste which I proudly serve to visitors and family and have done for as long as  I can remember- a family tradition!
Results.Title: Refill Make more sense

Results.ReviewText: original = the only coffee we have, no matter what, we cannot start the day without it. Refill pack is a marvellous idea - easy to carry and no extra jar in the cupboard, saving room and the environment - points all round!
Results.Title: The best

Results.ReviewText:
My Dad, now deceased, turned me on to Nescafe Original. It was the ONLY coffee he'd drink, & the only person allowed to make it for him was my Mum (happily, still with us) - so I remember him with every cup!
Thanks, Dad!
Results.Title: The Original And Best

Results.ReviewText: I always buy this coffee when it's on Special offer in the supermarket. I find it uniquely flavoursome when taken without milk or sugar. It kickstarts the new day like nothing else when taken first thing at breakfast time
Results.Title: Indispensable

Results.ReviewText: Good value for money. Really intense flavour, great pick me up. I love it made with some warm milk! We have been using this brand of coffee for over 30 years although have tried others but always come back to our Nescafé.
Results.Title: Great everyday coffee

Results.ReviewText: Of all the granulated coffees' currently on the market, 'Original' is now the closest to grinding the beans and getting the 'Bodum' out of the cupboard and cleaning it afterwards. Just as nice, but a lot more convenient!
Results.Title: I've tried a lot and this was the best

Results.ReviewText:
Every morning if I don't my Nescafé original is like put my shoes on withou socks. 
Specially in those early morning after a late night shift. It always do the trick. Keep me awake and warm me up too. 
Amazing product.
Results.Title: Always do the trick !

Results.ReviewText:
My parents have ways had this coffee so not only does it taste amazing but it reminds me of home. 
Lovely flavour, affordable and easily avaliable in most of not all supermarkets means it's a great coffee for everyday!!
Results.Title: Perfect start to the day

Results.ReviewText: I've been drinking Nescafe original for years and years. It's always the same good quality. I drink about 3 or 4 mugs every day. Half an inch of semi-skimmed milk (milk in first!), no sugar. Simple, quick and convenient.
Results.Title: Consistently good

Results.ReviewText: I do not have other coffees apart from Nescafe. I have tried others but have to come back as it is unique to taste. Recently tried the Intenso but that is once in awhile unlike the Original which is daily, works for me.
Results.Title: Hits the spot every time

Results.ReviewText: I bought a jar two weeks ago, as this blend is the choice at work for staff and customers.Always make with freshly boiled water to get the best of the rich  and smooth taste. Always use cold milk to keep the best taste.
Results.Title: Smooth and rich blend in an instant!

Results.ReviewText: I love the rich flavour of original Nescafé - I keep getting my head turned by fancy new coffees but always come back to this one.  Lovely unique flavour with no bitterness at all.  Still love it after all these years.
Results.Title: Still my favourite!

Results.ReviewText: Always had Nescafe - different vessels but always Nescafe - the smell of a freshly opened jar encapsulates the just brewed cup of coffee to come accompanied by croissant or a full English ..... puts the ahhhh in ahhhh
Results.Title: Extra sensory smell

Results.ReviewText: I use this coffee in work. The whole office loves it. The taste has been changed and it gives a creamy but satisfying coffee taste. It suits for all needs whether it's strong or weak. Will always use this coffee now.
Results.Title: Great new taste

Results.ReviewText: Straight forward, no nonsense coffee. Simple to make and of course you can vary the strength and add what you like to your own taste. Strong with a splash of milk does it for me. Better to buy in a refill style bag.
Results.Title: Original, Good, Hits the spot

Results.ReviewText: My family have been using nescafe original for years, whilst I am more of a Nescafe Gold fan, I would still drink the original when I am home and find that it is the same as ever - good, strong cup of instant coffee
Results.Title: Does what it says on the tin

Results.ReviewText: I have been using this granular coffee for many a year and I have never been able to find another product that gives such flavour and convenience. Many have tried and many have failed to copy, Nescafé are the best.
Results.Title: Nescafé original WOW

Results.ReviewText: Nescafe Original is my favourite instant coffee.It is the only brand of instant coffee I buy because out of all the co offers I have tried it is the only one that gives the full bodied roasted flavour that I love.
Results.Title: Rich, smooth and satisfying

Results.ReviewText: I always insist on original UK labelled Nescafe, and sure enough it provides the assurance of a quality standard cup of satisfying coffee. Don't pick up the imported Nescafe because it just doesn't taste the same.
Results.Title: Consistent Good Standard Coffee

Results.ReviewText: Flavour aroma and taste may have changed, like most other things we have to get used to it. I suppose once I overcome the. "New " sensations, I would continue to enjoy it more than ever,. Long live the new Nescafé
Results.Title: Old vs New

5345a1a9-0d19-4fca-aaae-bf7f6c72efdd.Name: Nescafé Original Refill

Results.Description: A well-rounded, smooth coffee with a rich aroma.
